title: Unibono Dog Grooming Clipper Kit, Quiet Cordless Pet Clipper for Dogs & Cats, Silent Dog Cat Shaver for Paws, Claws, Eyes, Ears, Face with Grooming Scissors Comb, Green
features: Pet Hair Grooming Kit for Thick Coats(Cockapoo Poodle dogs & cats): Unibono pet hair clipper kit has medium body & 40mm titanium ceramic blades, which can help you trim long body hair and reach smaller narrower areas like paws, ears and eyes with less effort. Its weight is more conducive to long-term holding and can provide you and your pets with a comfortable and precise trimming experience.

Multiple Cutter Heads & Multi-functions: Unibono dog and cat grooming kit adopts detachable design with 4 replaceable cutter heads— standard cutter head, narrow cutter head, small(details) cutter head and nail grinder head, which can be quickly replaced with just one pull & one push to meet the needs of dog and cat body trimming.

Silent & Cordless: The noise level of this dog clipper is about 55dp during working, quiet motor achieved the perfect balance between powerful cutting and low-noise operation. Whether it is trimming the hair on the claws or eye sockets, everything will be done easily. USB charging design allows you to trim pets anytime, anywhere, making them love hair styling!

Strong Power & IPX7 Waterproof: Driven by upgraded heavy-duty 7000RPM motor, brings a snag-free cutting to your pets' grooming work, combined with the sharp ceramic blades, it can provide excellent cutting performance and greatly reduce the discomfort of your pet. And the IPx7 waterproof level allows you to wash directly in water, making your cleaning and maintenance more convenient and fast. Besides, we packaged ONE extra blade for standard cutting head as replacement.

Novice Friendly & Tips: Exquisite package includes 4 standard attachment guide comb(3, 6, 9, 12 mm), a narrow attachment guide comb, a small(details) attachment guide comb and stainless steel comb and scissor. You can freely control the length of pet hair as needed by attach guide comb, even if you have never used it before. It is recommended to bathe and dry your dogs and cats first before grooming.

NOTE: Please give a bath to your lovely pets before hair grooming. And use the metal scissors & comb(in the package) to cut off the matted or overlong hair first and then use the trimmer for a smooth styling.
After-service: Your satisfaction is always our top priority. If you got any question during use, please feel free to contact us. We're 24 hours online for you!
